# Request form (CTA) — Web3Forms (client-side submission).
#
# Web3Forms' free tier requires submitting from the browser, so the access key
# is exposed client-side — this is BY DESIGN and safe: the key only permits
# submitting to the mapped inbox, never reading anything, and the recipient
# email address itself is never present (Web3Forms maps it to the key).
#
# Get a free key: enter the owner's email at https://web3forms.com → copy the key.
# Set it in the Vercel project (it is inlined into the client bundle at build):
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=
